ikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22134939/Kingdom-Vendetta-x3.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22134939/Kingdom-Vendetta-x3-297x176.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22134939/Kingdom-Vendetta-x3-800x475.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22134939/Kingdom-Vendetta-x3-120x71.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22134939/Kingdom-Vendetta-x3-768x456.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>This <a href=\"https://www.tftuned.com/2021-vendetta-x3/p3974\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">enduro hardtail </a>comes in with a few upgrades from the previous model, including updated geometry with 27.5 and 29″ wheel specific geos. This is currently available in small, medium, and large, starting at £1,300.</p><h3>The Rudy Project Crossway Helmet</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.rudyprojectna.com/collections/helmets/products/crossway?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22135555/Rudy-Project-Crossway-Helmet.jpg\" alt=\"Rudy Project Crossway Helmet\" width=\"1200\" height=\"744\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22135555/Rudy-Project-Crossway-Helmet.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22135555/Rudy-Project-Crossway-Helmet-297x184.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22135555/Rudy-Project-Crossway-Helmet-800x496.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22135555/Rudy-Project-Crossway-Helmet-120x74.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22135555/Rudy-Project-Crossway-Helmet-768x476.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Customers love that <a href=\"https://www.rudyprojectna.com/collections/helmets/products/crossway?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">this helmet</a> provides the necessary level of protection with a low weight, built-in bug net, and typical Rudy Project style. If you’re looking for something lighter that will still keep your noggin safe, grab one for $130 while it’s in stock.</p><p>In case you missed it, click <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/16/available-now/\">here</a> to check out what was back in stock last time.</p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Harley Schafer","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"ebc1fc671f9d0efdba98b873c2255adc45a46bee1fe16fd3dd0953b7b109e2c0","category":"Cycling"}